<section>

<h2>Doconce: abstract  <a name="___sec11"></a></h2>

<p>

<!-- code=text typeset with pygments style "emacs" -->
<div class="highlight" style="background: #f8f8f8"><pre style="line-height: 125%">__Abstract.__
Here goes the abstract...
</pre></div>
